OL,3,CExhibition of Japanese silk
OL,4,Cembroideries opens in Guernsey
OL,6,FA Guernsey embroiderer has opened her
OL,7,Ffirst solo exhibition in Saumaurez
OL,8,FPark's Folk Museum.
OL,10,FBetty Watson's 'Traditional Japanese
OL,11,FEmbroidery In Silk' exhibition
OL,12,Fshowcases several pieces she's created
OL,13,Fover the past 25 years.
OL,15,FBetty says: "I've enjoyed it I've had
OL,16,Flots of fun doing it and it's nice to
OL,17,Fbe able to encourage others to do it.
OL,19,F"It's beautiful that's the main thing
OL,20,Fand it's lovely silk."
