OL,3,CExhibition of Japanese silk
OL,4,Cembroideries opens in Guernsey
OL,6,FTo create traditional Japanese
OL,7,Fembroidery, artists must master 46
OL,8,Fdifferent stitch techniques.
OL,10,FBetty travelled to France and England
OL,11,Fto hone her craft and learn from other
OL,12,Fembroiderers.
OL,14,FThe display of her Japanese silk
OL,15,Fembroideries will run from Tuesday 24
OL,16,FSeptember until Friday 25 October.
OL,18,FBetty said the support for her
OL,19,Fexhibition has been "quite amazing"
OL,20,Fand she hopes that her work will
OL,21,Finspire others to take up the art.
