OL,6,FShe adds: "Japanese embroidery is a
OL,7,Fcontinuation of a thousand-year-old
OL,8,Ftradition that first began in China
OL,9,Fthen spread to Japan and more recently
OL,10,Fto other countries around the world.
OL,12,F"This has been my passion for over 20
OL,13,Fyears."
